lead_paragraph: Damion Lee scored 17 points, Anas Mahmoud added 15 and No. 17 Louisville held on in the closing seconds to beat hard-luck Georgia Tech 75-71 on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Lee, Mahmoud Lead No. 17 Louisville Past Georgia Tech 75-71
